title: Pearhead Classic Wooden Letterboard, Baby Keepsake Clip Photo Frame, Wooden
features: Trendy and fun, Pearhead letterboard photo fame is the perfect addition to your baby's nursery
Includes 294 black letters, numbers, and symbols to personalize; also includes an easel to sit on any tabletop or triangle hanger for easy wall mounting
Rustic, whitewashed wooden frame. Use the silver clip to hang your sonogram picture
A perfect way to share your ultrasound photo and baby announcement - and then continue to share your baby milestones after your little one arrives
Dimensions: 8" W x 8" H x .5" D// Photo insert: 4" X 5"
description: Pearhead’s Letterboard Photo Frame is the perfect addition to your baby’s nursery! This whitewashed, rustic frame includes a silver clip to display a 4" X 5" photo. Below the photo includes a letterboard area to add in cute, fun phrases! Use the 294 black letters, numbers, and symbols to personalize with your own messages. Have fun choosing your favorite photo of your baby and adding in a cute phrase. Display a sonogram photo and fill in details about your due date or add a photo of your newborn baby with their name and birthday. Use the included easel to display on any tabletop or hang on any wall with the triangle hanger. You can also use this frame as a special way to deliver a message! Display your sonogram photo and gift it to family to announce your pregnancy! Everyone will love this clever way to share messages! And don’t forget to add to your registry. Not expecting but know someone who is? This letterboard photo frames makes the perfect gift! You can open it up and spell out your own congratulatory message before gifting! Product dimensions: 8" W x 8" H x 0.5" D; Photo insert: 4" x 5".
